                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On November 3, the Policy Planning Staff discussed international control of
                    atomic energy, the possible development of the hydrogen bomb, and related
                    problems with the Secretary of State, Under Secretary Webb, and other
                    Departmental officials. For the minutes of that meeting, see <ref target="#pg_573">page 573</ref>.</p>
            </div>
